Pros
- multiple users
- automated discovery of their sleep traits
- intelegent suggestions based on their sleep traits and pools data
- due to separation the llm logic from telegram interface, it is easier to add new interfaces
- messages are scheduled daily, from the next day 12pm till the time of flight - 20 minutes

only meaningful messages (parsing states are scipped) are passed to the LLM memory, so it can track only the most important information


